divs: Sighting DetailsIt was about 7.30 in the morning. I walked with a couple of horses to a meadow. And then I saw an orange coloured "H"that made a nose dive pulled up and disappeared in the clouds. It was just beside my house. I don't know what it was. Not an airplane nor a reflection.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Roermond
This sighting has never been favorited.
